headline: General Motors (NYSE:GM) Extends Strategic Partnership With Malibu Boats For Engine Innovation
summary: General Motors (NYSE:GM) recently extended its collaboration with Malibu Boats, designating Chevrolet as the Official Vehicle Brand of Malibu Boats, which underscores GM's innovative engagement in diverse sectors. Over the last quarter, GM's stock price moved 2.7% lower, amid a flat market backdrop and various corporate changes including new executive appointments. headline: Why Forecasters Can’t Agree On When Oil Demand Will Peak
summary: Oil demand is proving more resilient than expected, with forecasts suggesting a plateau rather than a sharp decline.
